(90065, UNKNOWN, UNKNOWN, 'I overestimated my strength. All of the dragons - even the Aspects themselves - have been greatly weakened since the fall of Deathwing.', 12, 0, 100, UNKNOWN, 0, 52876, '93114', 'Stellagosa to Player'),
